I: Initialize

Close task and go online

Call message box "confirmation only" (SP0016)
When multiple matching records are found allow user to choose one
Update confirmed schedule,
Close task and reinitialize
(if user does not choose, cycle record level)
End "Confirmation Only"
Check for duplicate schedule entry if no unconfirmed records found
Call MsgBox "Possible duplicate schedule" (SP0017) >>OK
Call OSP003 to allow user to determine duplicity
Call MsgBox "Confirm new schedule" (SP0018) >>Yes/No/Cancel
MsgBoxRet=Y: User confirms schedule as New
Set flag and allow handling as if no matches were found
MsgBoxRet=N: User decides schedule was already entered
Discard changes (reinitialize)
MsgBoxRet=C: User Cancels confirmation
Return online
End "duplication check"

Fetch New ID and create entries
Close transaction and reinitialize
End "New Schedule"

End "Save"
